        "Another analysis focuses on popular restaurants based on the number of reviews. Restaurants that receive a large number of reviews are usually more popular or frequently visited. Identifying such restaurants can help understand which businesses attract the most customer attention. Similarly, the project also examines popular cuisines by counting how frequently different cuisine types appear in the dataset. This helps in understanding customer preferences and trending food categories.\n",
